<div><head>《零陵先賢傳》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-1a.2">《劉巴》</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-1a.3">劉先生欲遣周不疑就劉巴學，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-1a.4">巴曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-1a.5">昔游荊北，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-1a.6">時涉師門，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-1a.7">記問之學，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-1a.8">不足紀名，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-1a.9">猶天之南箕，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-1a.10">虛而不用，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-1a.11">賜書乃欲賢甥摧鸞鳳之翮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-1a.12">游燕雀之宇，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-1a.13">將何以啟明之哉？<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-2a.2">《鄭產》</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-2a.3">鄭產，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-2a.4">零陵人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-2a.5">為白土鄉嗇夫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-2a.6">時民家產子一歲，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-2a.7">輒出口錢，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-2a.8">以故貧家鮮有舉子者。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-2a.9">產勸百姓勿殺子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-2a.10">口錢皆為代出，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-2a.11">郡縣具以聞上，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-2a.12">錢因得免，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-2a.13">改白土曰更生生鄉。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-3a.2">《葉譚》</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-3a.3">葉譚，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-3a.4">字令思，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-3a.5">零陵人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-3a.6">少負節操，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-3a.7">未幾舉孝廉。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-3a.8">王濟謂譚曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-3a.9">君吳楚人也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-3a.10">亡國之餘，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-3a.11">有何秀異而應斯舉？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-3a.12">譚曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-3a.13">君不聞明珠大貝，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-3a.14">獨生江海之濱乎？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-3a.15">為之武子默然。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-4a.2">《蔡倫》</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-4a.3">蔡倫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-4a.4">字仲敬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-4a.5">零桂人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-4a.6">少負才，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-4a.7">官常侍，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1343_CHANT_001-4a.8">造紙有聲。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
